item.description: Organizing Expert & Life Coach Sibel Babacan (aka our very own Dr.Bee) will be leading a discussion on the Top 10 Organizing Dilemmas for busy families and what to do about them. We will also talk about common organizing mistakes and simple, creative solutions to overcome them. This will be an informal meeting during which members will be invited to share their own challenges and success stories, as well.
item.name: Discussion: Keen to Conquer Your Clutter?
